Definition: `furthest' is used more often than `farthest' in this abstract sense)
Example: went the furthest of all the children in her education; furthest removed from reality; she goes farthest in helping us
Synonyms: farthest, to, the, greatest, degree, or, extent, most, advanced, stage, is, used, more, often, than, in, this, abstract, sense, went, of, all, children, her, education, removed, from, reality, she, goes, helping, us
Category: adv.all
